<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Khuonga</author>
<hymn_number>295</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Muot theia tuh a um,
 Muot theilo lo a tho di'n;
 Limbawl loha tuh in I um,
 Lopi taka kaihthawh dingin. (2)

[V2]
 2. Hatlo a tuh a um,
 Thilhih theia tho di'n;
 Taksaa tuhin I um ui,
 Thagau a thodawk kit ding in (2)

[V3]
 3. Lei taksa a chuoma,
 Van taksa a chuom hi,
 Lei lopina a danglama;
 Thagau lopina a dang hi, (2)

[V4]
 4. Lalpa chu Aw gi tawh,
 Vansawlchak lopi tawh;
 Pengkun in ei hun sam intin,
 Lalpa kawma chun chawl dingin. (2)

[V5]
 5. Thihna um ta puon tin,
 Kahna um ta puona;
 Thihna gun eizo ta puona;
 Melma nunung I nuoisieh tau. (2)</lyrics>
<title>Muot Thei A Tuh A Um !</title>
</song>